\f0\fs32 \cf0 Kartik is a qualified civil engineer from the College of Engineering Pune and holds a postgraduate degree in management from Pune University. He spent his formative years living in a variety of locations across India as his father, who worked for the Indian government, was transferred from place to place. He is a voracious reader who loves reading history, fiction and biographies. He likes listening to music and is a crack ace at all racket sports.
